summary: This is a simple mod that allows you to create erotic art with Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
This mod is used for creating erotic art with Skyrim.

With this mod you can make unlimited erotic positions and you can manually add as many animations as you want from any adult skyrim mod.

Update: people have been asking me questions.
Please note that I made a tutorial video and a description of how the mod works. You can find the tutorial video and description in the mod folder.
author: Bram
